address.streetAddress: Poppey Bonus Room Plan, Prairie Meadows

location.fullValue: Poppey Bonus Room Plan, Prairie Meadows

data.description: Gorgeous home on 3/4 acre lot in highly sought after Deer Creek School District. Home boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms on the main floor, along with formal dining and open-concept kitchen/living room. Upstairs is a huge bonus room (could be 5th bedroom) with full bath and walk in closet. Split plan allows privacy in the primary suite with all other bedrooms on the opposite side of the house. Outside is a pure oasis with an in-ground pool with waterfall, a pergola for added shade and access to a private half bathroom.  Schedule your showing on this beauty today!
